_sText:
This is my deathrun map, it is very funny and special, because every CT spawns with a jetpack.
He can use it by holding left mouse, then he gets an upwards boost.

At the beginning the map seems impossible, but after some practise you can beat it under 3 min (or less).

T's have a improved version of the CTs jetpack

This map has 64 CT spawns and 2 T spawns

In the end you can choose between Bhop, HE, Knife and Laser duell (and if you are fast enough you can even instantly kill the Ts or go to the Ts region)



Have fun

PS: I've used this textures http://www.fpsbanana.com/textures/707
